i just woke up and am bored so here's an update on my life for all of those people out there who don't care

- i have a job now, i start the 18th at panera bread..... nothing great but it's money and i can look for a better job while i'm working there
- I'm going to a couple of doctors over the next couple of months for testing on a bunch of stuff, there's a good possibility i might have lyme disease... which   would kind of be awesome because it would explain a lot about me being sick all the time and a lot of other problems i have
- i have to go to the pediatrist on a regular basis now b/c i have been walking funny on my one foot since i messed up my ankle a couple years back and   now that foot is starting to hurt a lot... i'm supposed to get some specially molded insoles or something but my insurance won't cover them and they're $300    without insurance so i'm on some pain killers right now and if those aren't working too well then i'm going to get cortazone (sp?) shots every two weeks in    my foot
- in april there is going to be the greatest road trip ever with some of the greatest people ever
- mean streets is sticking in there.... a couple of shows coming up within the next couple of weeks
- I'm going to try and start volunteering at the humane society of charlotte and my family might also get an awesome little boxer/pit bull mix from there named   charlotte, she's white with a couple little brown spots and blue eyes and is deaf
- Going to shows with no money and leaving with money is awesome and has happened twice this weekend
- I'm really thankful for my friends and this weekend has been the greatest, there's nothing better than just going out of town and hanging out and acting half   your age it helps make me forget that i'm almost 22 and almost done with college
- shelter is awesome 
- that's pretty much it

k so thanks to everyone who came friday.......... it was an amazing show minus the tad bit of dumb drama.......... that new venue is AWESOME........ i'm excited to have more shows there......... but yeah as for right now... fuck studying, and fuck physics........ this shit sucks.......... on another note the movie in good company is pretty good, same with the scottish movie sweet sixteen (even though you don't understand what they're saying for most of the movie)

so the last couple of days have been hectic with school and stuff....... i feel almost dead........ but still tomorrow will be awesome..... i'd appreciate anyone's attendance tomorrow night.... my parents and my sister are coming..... so that's cool....... but yeah.... it'd be great to send this band off with a bang..... a lot of good times have come with it but it's time for it to end..... we kind of just got stuck and weren't getting anywhere different.... but oh well how it's ending is sad but you know shit happens..... sometimes you have to just keep going....... i just hope that people actualy come out to this... it'd be nice to see a large crowd in charlotte at somewhere that isn't tremont..... i have high hopes for this new venue and hope that maybe going to shows can be fun again..... that maybe this'll spark some new life and that new people will start coming out and that maybe i can go to a show without getting kicked out...... especially the getting kicked out part... i'm sick of that.......
i've been thinking a lot lately about where i'm going in life....... and then i thought about it really hard and figured out that i don't really care.... and i don't really see any point in caring.... i mean why spend all my time worrying about what's going to happen and miss all that is happening... the last couple of months have had some amazing times..... i'm really thankful for the new friends i've made and the old ones that've stuck around... lots planned for this winter..... hopefully it will beat out the endless summer and be better..... 


but yeah on a final note come out tomorrow night....... we'll try to make it worth your $5

Man so this week........ i just wish i didn't have to work..... then i'd have a 5 day weekend....... and it'd be awesome.......  oh well i really need the money...  this weekend wasn't bad..... just wasn't too eventful........ but yeah.... practice was...... well practice..... got two new cover songs and hopefully another one next practice..... everyone should come out December 2nd for the last show...... this is for real though...... not just some of my bullshit...... i really don't want to go work today but i have to....... so i'm off

so the last two days have been awesomeeeeeeeeeeee............. one not having to get up to go to work on saturday is cool as hell........ anddddddddd bonfires are the shit.... so are walks around rancid ponds..... anddddddddddddddd h2o and stretcharm strong.... at tremont........ get sikeeeeeeeed
so the new with honor... not that bad...... still think the split with the distance was amillion times better
uncc's website has to be the biggest piece of shit ever made.............
Thousands of lives are on hold right now........ but to be honest i think i enjoy playing pacman more

<u>north davidson street</u> friday was fun..... it was nice to do something that didn't involve sitting around someone's house..... nice to have a change in scenary.... then saturday i finally got to go to brooklyn south and get some good pizza.. and i even saw nelbo and chase there....... fun times..... and then yesterday it was bro night at the hockey game....... which was a blast....... even though i liked independance arena a million times better..... the new place is too clean and like it's huge.... the game itself was a really good game and the checkers blew sc away.. it ended up being 7-2... and yes there were some really good fights too.........i really had a fun time and hope there are more trips to games to come....... like the most expensive tickets are $22...... so i think we neeed to start just getting tons of people to go........ on another note i definately just failed my test in my film class... what realllllly sucks is that i didn't fail b/c i didn't know the material...... i totally knew the material....... it was just that we had an hour to write three essays and i didn't get them all done...... oh well..... i think i'm going to go talk to my teacher wednesday about it.... and see if there's maybe something i can do to make it up...... i have to be to work at 12 today.... i really don't feel like going..... i want to go have an adventure..... but i have to go b/c i need money..... and then after that i need to go buy some stuff from the auto store b/c last night i went to adjust my rear view mirror and it just straight fell off..... which sucks..... so i need to get that fixed asap..... and then ihave to come home and get some reading done and probably watch some movies....... if anyone wants to do anything this week though let me know......

so i finally have a night were i don't have to do a bunch of stuff and i feel sick as hell...... i feel super hot and my head is pounding...... i think i'm just going to go do some laundry and go catch up on some needed sleep....... seriously group work is the dumbest idea ever..... my stupid group was dumb... they can't even email a file to someon right..... oh well whatever...... it's done with..... maybe now ican calm down and not be so frustrated and stressed out about everything.... well atleast till sunday when i have to study for my tests i have next week....

so this weekend was awesome aside from a little bit of drama........ and now it's halloween....... which is awesome...... except for the fact i have so much school work to do tonight that i can't do shit....... but oh well the weekend's been too good to be down about anything.......  so i'm going to sit here and listen to the misfits and write my paper and do my presentation...... but first i need some grub.... i should've snagged some free penara bread things from moshelle b/c we don't have shit here and i have no money...... like or atleast i have nothing that matches... like peanut butter and no jelly...... salsa but no chips... cereal but no milk.....  maybe there'll be some sweet movies on tv tonight.... if anyone's not doing anythign they should come over and watch some with me

this cold weather is awesome!!!!!!!!!!

oh yeah and watching horror movies all night is too

so yeah....... waiting was hillarious (even though i still stand by the fact that andy miliahwkh;lsawhatever is dumb and not funny) and everyone should see it.... but yeah.... i have like 15 minutes till i have to walk to class.... yeah i've actualy started going like every day now..... i think i completely screwed myself allready but i am in the process of trying to get that fixed..... i wish i had time to make another mix tape b/c the one i have right now is getting boring b/c it's been all i've been listening to.....yeah so my ac has been broke meaning it's been hot as hell in here everynight even though it's fall........ they're supposed to come fix it today.... so far this place has been pretty good about getting stuff fixed.... i also need a haircut super bad..... and now i'm going to school, b/c that's what college kids do.. haha and on a sidenote this one guy at work decided to start calling me professor??? whats up with the people i work with?
mp tonight at tremont... if you're not doing something come out..... if you are doing something come out anyways..... party afterwards.. come to that too

shit so i just got woken up by an amazing phone call that totally made my month...... but now i'm wide awake... and i have to be to work early as hell.... and not a single person is online except for my mom...... hahaha what are the odds of that.....
so this is the first day with no migraines in a long time..... not even a headache today..... hopefully that's a good sign and hopefully it stays that way..... and tgi fridays is the best
so yesterday was awesome..... today wasn't the best day... but it happens

yeah so today should be awesome...... i'm about to head over to work for 4.5 hours and do my time there......... and then it's off to sc for the unseen, global threat, and mp................. i'm excited..... should be a fun trip....... and as for tomorrow i have nothing to do other than go pick up the stephanies from school so if anyone wants to hang out...... i want to make the most of the day and not waste it all sleeping

so i finally got to go to sleep wiithout an alarm clock set... it was a good feeling..... i didn't wake up ever ten minutes like i usually do..... i feel really rested.... but like i slept weird and my neck and back hurt really bad and i have a migraine again... but i feel rested for the first time in a while........

so a while back i used to have trouble actualy getting to sleep...... that doesn't seem to be a problem anymore........ now it's more so finding time to sleep and when i'm actualy asleep getting rest....... it seems like everytime i wake up i feel even more tired.... what in the hell... i mean seriously..... that's not how it's supposed to work........  the dead pets were awesome........ the corpse bride was awesome....... work sucked........ school sucked......... man seriously class seems like it was like 15 days ago instead of like 15 hours ago....... today's been long as hell...... i need some sleep.....

so i'm back from pa and not much seems to have changed while i'm gone...... my room is still a mess, i'll probably clean when i get back from work..................... and i now need to go to work.........

masfd;klasjgkjag/............ god damnit.......... my eye is like 3 times as swollen as it was yesterday........ this really sucks..... well i have to go get medicine for it now b/c i can barely see out of my left eye now

awesome.......... i forgot how awesome of a movie beetlejuice is............. 3 days left till i leave

went out last night
then i got back and actualy decided to hang out downstairs, it really wasn't that bad, i had fun..... and mike d showed up which was awesome.....
it sounds like people are still downstairs...... i need to clean up around here, it's a mess....... and then i'm probably going to go spend some time with my sister and family before it gets too late... then i think i'm going to will's to see him since he's back...... hopefully it'll be fun.....

only 5 days left
someone should donate a vcr to me...... i only own two dvds......... and like i don't feel like having to always go downstairs to watch movies

kalhdfjg;agjs god i hate life sometimes........................................................... but yeah anyways.... umm....... today was allright for the most part....... shitty parts......... good parts............. tomorrow i get to walk to school at like 7........ suckssssssssssssssssssssssssss........... but yeah stupid labs............ ummm............ so next thursday i leave for PA and won't be back till sunday night......... oh yeah and this saturday party at the lake........ if you want to come talk to me somehow....... alsoooooo umm more people should come over and hang out.... only like 3 people have seen my apartment......... um so tom petty i think is one of the coolest people in the world........... and i'll take his word that even losers get lucky some time...... but i have to be upearly as hell..... but oh well........

i feel like absolute shit....... i need a hobby..... or something to keep me from sleeping so much...... i feel like i'm half dead..... but oh well i'm excited b/c i get tara's letter tomorrow.... and then there's fun time tomorrow night...... yeah tonight kind of sucked b/c i felt/feel like shit........ there's a party going on downstairs but i don't feel like haning out so i think i'm going to just read........ k bye

oh yeah on a side note... i woke up this mornign to my computer being completely fucked........ like nothign would open...... so i restarted it and like then mcafee would not stop with the little pop ups about unwanted programs on my computer...... it was insane...... so yeah hopefully it will work fine now........ 


man this mac and cheese sucks

so i slept yesterday forever.......i started naping at like 3 or 4 till about 8 this morning occasionally getting up for maybe 10 or 20 minutes and then just laying back down......... what a horrible idea................. i feel like absolute shit now..... oh welll.......... i have to scarf down my mac and cheese and then go to class and then run home... eat more (i missed lunch and dinner last night so that probably doesn't hlep with the whole feeling good thing)... then run to work and then run to the bank (i'll have money that i just have to go buy books with)... and then go pick up joe and sara and then we're going to come back here and hang out, if anyone else wants to they are more than welcome to
